1500:〔Nanami〕“Ever since I woke up this morning, my right hand's been throbbing a little bit.”\p;
1600:Which was real?\n;Which was a delusion?\p;
1700:What was I looking at?\n;Who had I been talking to until now?\p;
1800:Where had that Nanami gone?\n;Where had this Nanami come from?\p;
1900:〔Nanami〕“Big Bro!”\p;
