2900:Caught between two Nanamis, I...\p;
3000:〔Takumi〕“This is a delusion...!”\p;
3100:...sank to the floor, clutching my head.\p;
3200:If this was a delusion, I wanted to wake up already.\n;I didn't want to see a delusion this horrifying...!\n;And yet, no matter how much I wanted to wake up, I couldn't get back to reality.\p;
3300:〔Nanami〕“Is she... a fake...?”\p;
3400:The bloodstained Nanami shifted and swayed.\n;She held on to her DI-sword... a sword both pitiful and sinister, with a height comparable to even her own.\p;
3500:〔Nanami〕“Why is this... fake with you...?”\p;
