4000:Which Nanami was real?\n;Which Nanami was fake?\p;
4100:Were they both real?\n;Were they both fake?\p;
4200:〔Nanami〕“I'll show you, you fake...”\p;
4300:〔Nanami〕“Get away from my big bro...!”\p;
