4500:〔Nanami〕“Aaah!”\p;
4600:Making no attempt to avoid it, Nanami froze in place.
4700:\n;It hit her head on.
4800:\n;The brutal, unforgiving edge of the DI-sword dug into her neck, and then...\p;
4900:Making no attempt to avoid it, Nanami froze in place. It hit her head on. The brutal, unforgiving edge of the DI-sword dug into her neck, and then...
