5300:There wasn't any doubt that Nanami had swung the DI-sword. And with that amount of force behind it, Nanami's head should've been blown clean off.\p;
5400:〔Nanami〕“I knew it... You really are a fake...”\p;
5500:〔Nanami〕“H-Huh...? What... How did I...?”\p;
5600:Stop...\p;
5700:〔Nanami〕“You're a fake, and you know it.”\p;
5800:〔Nanami〕“I'm not a fake!”\p;
5900:Shut up already...\p;
6000:〔Nanami〕“Big Bro, get away! Get away from them!”\p;
6100:〔Nanami〕“She's wrong, Big Bro! I'm right here—you <i>k</i><i>n</i><i>o</i><i>w</i> I'm right here!”\p;
6200:〔Takumi〕“Sh-Shut the hell up!”\p;
6300:I couldn't help but scream.\n;It was all just so goddamn <i>c</i><i>o</i><i>n</i><i>f</i><i>u</i><i>s</i><i>i</i><i>n</i><i>g</i><i>!</i>\p;
6400:〔Takumi〕“One of you is a delusion...”\p;
6500:〔Takumi〕“My sister isn't... Nanami isn't... two different people...”\p;
6600:I alternated between the two Nanamis, comparing them.\n;Both looked like Nanami to me.\n;So I turned to the one wearing my sweatshirt.\p;
6700:I wished from the bottom of my heart...\n;That this Nanami was real.\p;
6800:That the Nanami I'd held tightly in my bed was real.\p;
6900:And so, I followed my desire.\n;I reached out my hand toward her face...\p;
7000:...all so I could gently brush her cheek...\p;
7100:...but...\p;
7200:...just like the DI-sword before me...\n;...my hand...\p;
7300:...slipped right through her.\p;
7400:Even though Nanami was right there.\n;I couldn't touch her.\n;I'd felt nothing there.\p;
7500:As if she were a holographic projection.\p;
7600:I was overwhelmed by an uncontrollable sadness.\n;Tears flooded from my eyes in large drops.\p;
7700:〔Nanami〕“No...”\p;
7800:〔Nanami〕“There's no way...”\p;
7900:〔Nanami〕“I'm not a fake...”\p;
8000:〔Nanami〕“C'mon, Big Bro... I'm not a fake, right...? Say I'm not a fake...”\p;
8100:Nanami tried to cling on to me.\n;And I tried to hold her in return.\p;
8200:And yet, just as I feared, the Nanami before me had no substance.\n;My hands slipped right through her body.\p;
8300:〔Nanami〕“This is wrong... This is all wrong...”\p;
8400:〔Nanami〕“I'm... I'm right here...!”\p;
8500:Nanami's right hand firmly grasped my left.\p;
8600:〔Takumi〕“Aah...”\p;
8700:I could feel it.\n;I could feel her frail strength grasping my hand.\p;
8800:I could feel neither her body, nor her head, nor her neck...\p;
8900:Only her right hand was touching me.\p;
9000:〔Nanami〕“Get away from him!”\p;
9100:The Nanami without a right hand shouted out.\p;
9200:〔Nanami〕“Get away from my big bro right now, you monster!”\p;
