9400:Sweat was pouring from that Nanami's forehead.\n;The color was draining from her face.\p;
9500:Considering her right hand had been cut off, and she was bleeding profusely, it was only a matter of time until she passed out.\p;
9600:An awful thought passed through my mind.\p;
9700:I knew it couldn't be true, but I couldn't stop myself from thinking about it.\n;In my mind, it was the only answer to all of this.\n;An answer... that was no less than a nightmare.\p;
9800:〔???〕“That's right...”\p;
