13400:〔Rimi〕“But I'm begging you... as painful as it may be...”\p;
13500:〔Rimi〕“...you need to face reality.”\p;
13600:〔Rimi〕“Stop this delusion right now, Taku.”\p;
13700:〔Nanami〕“Big Bro... Don't erase me...”\p;
13800:〔Rimi〕“If... you don't stop this delusion...”\p;
