14000:〔Nanami〕“Big Bro...!”\p;
14100:I shook off Nanami's right hand.\p;
14200:It was all too much...\n;I couldn't take it anymore.\p;
14300:I didn't have the slightest clue what to believe.\p;
14400:Believing Rimi's explanation? I just couldn't...\p;
14500:Believing Nanami, who was standing there in tears? I just couldn't...\p;
14600:Believing Nanami, who was lying there, grasping a DI-sword? I just couldn't...\p;
14700:Believing myself, and what I felt? I just couldn't...\p;
14800:What I wished for was something simple.\n;A quiet, peaceful life, with nothing to disturb it.\n;A wonderful, blissful future with Nanami—with my sister.\p;
14900:That was all I wished for.\n;That was all I hoped for.\p;
15000:Was I not allowed that wish?\n;Was I not allowed that hope?\p;
15100:Then...\p;
