15800:The world jolted.\p;
15900:〔Rimi〕“The Third Melt?!”\p;
16000:My wish had come true.\n;The world was enveloped in white.\n;All and everything was consumed by it.\p;
16100:And, as literally as could be... it was all erased.\p;
